[{"content":" 磁星乎 蓝星也\n尽毕生所学 未能察其分毫\n丈量其尺寸 悉知何物\n吾虽愚笨 不愿弃矣\n尽己所能 死而后已\n","date":"2025-12-02T17:00:00Z","image":"https://xiesl97.github.io/p/00-zhongqingshu/cover_hu_36609418d4973197.jpg","permalink":"https://xiesl97.github.io/p/00-zhongqingshu/","title":"钟情疏"},{"content":"\u0026ldquo;Meotor\u0026rdquo; 这个名字源自英文单词 Meteor (流星)\n","date":"2025-12-11T00:00:00Z","permalink":"https://xiesl97.github.io/p/01-meotor_name_origin/","title":"Meotor：名字的由来"}]